These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, sprite, water
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, daffodil, lily, amaryllis
1. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3
3. the person who growspoppy is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the person who growsamaryllis##5
5. the person who growspoppy is the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the person drinking sprite is the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Beverage      | water  | hot-chocolate | lemonade  | sprite |
| Flower   | lily | amaryllis      | poppy | daffodil |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, egyptian, italian, malaysian
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, r&b, funk, punk
1. the egyptian is between the fan of disco and the fan of punk##2
2. the malaysian is somewhere to the left of the fan of punk##5
3. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of funk##1
4. the fan of disco is on the right of the malaysian##1
5. the fan of r&b is on the left of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Nationality   | malaysian | italian | egyptian   | australian |
| Music-Genre           | funk      | disco    | r&b | punk      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
4 different pets are kept: snake, guinea-pig, hedgehog, horse
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, car, quad-bike, train
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the train is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5
4. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
5. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the right of the person driving the train##5
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Pet        | guinea-pig | snake | hedgehog     | horse |
| Transport   | car  | train   | quad-bike | bus    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, trance, folk, metal
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, epic, family, romance
1. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of trance##1
2. the fan of metal is somewhere to the right of the person watching family movies##5
3. the fan of gospel is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching epic movies##2
4. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
5. the person watching romance movies is the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Music-Genre         | folk | gospel | trance | metal |
| Movie-Genre   | romance   | family     | epic    | crime       |

