.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, corn, eggplant, kale
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, quad-bike, taxi, snowmobile
1. the person eating kale is somewhere to the left of the person driving the van##5
2. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3
3. the person eating eggplant is somewhere to the left of the person eating banana##5
4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the van##1
5. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3
6. the person eating kale is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| Food          | eggplant | kale   | banana   | corn    |
| Transport   | quad-bike  | snowmobile | van | taxi |

