.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-8::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, mango, pear, strawberry
House: craftsman, cape-cod, tower, wooden
1. the cape-cod house is on the right of the wooden house##1
2. the person eating strawberry is somewhere to the left of the tower house##5
3. the person eating strawberry is on the left or right of the person eating pear##3
4. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
5. the tower house is somewhere to the left of the craftsman house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food   | mango     | strawberry | pear     | carrot   |
| House    | wooden | cape-cod  | tower | craftsman |

