3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the victorian house##5
5. the ranch-style house is somewhere to the right of the craftsman house##5
6. the craftsman house is somewhere to the left of the tower house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |  4   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | iced-tea | milk   | cola |
| House       | craftsman       | tower   | victorian | ranch-style |

