2. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the left of the person who growssunflower##5
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the right of the person who growslily##5
4. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
5. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |   3    |     4      |
| Flower   | lily | tulip       | balloon-flower   | sunflower        |
| Sport      | surfing  | weightlifting | soccer | water-polo |

