.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-11::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, kale, cranberry, lime
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, parkour, soccer, water-polo
1. the person eating cabbage is somewhere to the left of the person eating kale##5
2. the person who's sport is soccer is the person eating cranberry##1
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person eating kale##1
4. the person eating lime is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##5
5. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##5
6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
7. the person eating cranberry is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4      |
| Food   | cabbage | kale   | cranberry | lime     |
| Sport   | parkour     | badminton | soccer  | water-polo |

