.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-15::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, rat, turtle, frog
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, entrepreneur, manager, mechanic
1. the owner of the frog is between the owner of the turtle and the owner of the rat##2
2. the analyst is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
3. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
4. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the right of the manager##5
5. the manager is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
6. the manager is on the left of the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |      3       |     4     |
| Pet   | goldfish | turtle  | frog      | rat |
| Job     | manager    | mechanic | entrepreneur | analyst   |

