.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-16::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, coral, brown, amber
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, electronic, gospel, hip-hop
1. the person who likes brown is in an even position##4
2. the person who likes amber is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who likes coral is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the fan of classical is in an even position##4
5. the person who likes light-blue is somewhere to the left of the person who likes amber##5
6. the person who likes brown is between the person who likes light-blue and the fan of electronic##2
7. the person who likes coral is somewhere to the right of the person who likes light-blue##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Color      | light-blue   | brown  | coral      | amber       |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | hip-hop | electronic | classical |

