.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-20::.
House: cape-cod, townhouse, craftsman, gothic-revival
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, ship, skateboard, snowmobile
1. the townhouse house is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
2. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5
5. the townhouse house is somewhere to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##5
6. the cape-cod house is between the gothic-revival house and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| House        | townhouse     | gothic-revival | cape-cod | craftsman |
| Transport   | skateboard | snowmobile | ship      | car        |

 